></iframe></p><p>在谈到曲目时，人们说：“从堕落的深处到流行的完美高度，康曼可以做到这一切，这次我们将伊丽莎（Eliza）带入了旅程。有人说这是我们迄今为止最愚蠢的事情，我们同意。”</p><p> DJ/制片人Rose补充说：“因此，与Fartent Officity的人相爱，与Fabbest，最炙手可热，最怪异的派对宝贝（Babes）成为同胞派对女孩的荣誉。录音室写作时，这是一个值得纪念的夜晚。我心康曼。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/confidence-man-3am-la-la-la-review-3801838"><i>NME</i> awarded &#39;3AM (LA LA LA )&#39; four stars upon its release in October</a> , writing: “Already the most fun live band around, you always feel that Confidence Man are on the precipice of becoming the kind of proper crossover pop stars that Bowen Yang might impersonate on <i>Saturday Night Live.</i> &#39;3AM (LA LA LA)&#39;, their most assured collection yet, proves they definitely have the tunes to match their outsized personas.”</p><p> It went on to be named as <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995"><i>NME</i> ’s 20th best album of 2024</a> . </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Confidence Man on Glastonbury 2024, new music and living in London" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PxyD47Irbd4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/confidence-man-interview-album-3am-la-la-glastonbury-3799222">The group spoke to <i>NME</i> ahead of its release</a> , with vocalist Janet Planet joking, “We&#39;re gonna be fucked for the fourth album. We&#39;ve used everything we have in this one.”</p><p> The Australian group are <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">nominated for International Group Of The Year at the Brit Awards</a> , which go down on Saturday (March 1), where they face competition from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amyl-and-the-sniffers">Amyl And The Sniffers</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">Future</a> / <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metro-boomin">Metro Boomin</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a> .</p><p> They will also be navigating the 2025 festival circuit, with appearances announced for <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/parklife-2025-full-lineup-announced-50-cent-charli-xcx-jorja-smith-100-more-3832474">Parklife</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/50-cent-biffy-clyro-and-snow-patrol-head-eye-catching-trnsmt-2025-festival-line-up-tickets-3818465">TRNSMT</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/confidence-man-shygirl-and-more-to-join-barry-cant-swim-at-all-points-east-2025-3811109">All Points East</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-confidence-mans-poptastic-new-single-i-heart-you-with-eliza-rose-3842463">Listen to Confidence Man&#39;s poptastic new single &#39;I Heart You&#39; with Eliza Rose</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
